Sam was interested in playing football in his early days and he still loves watching them. He started dating <strong><em>Laura Haddock</em></strong> and extended their relationship by getting married to each other in 2013.Laura and Sam wound up as a pleased guardian to a son and they are expecting a second child soon. <strong><em>Laura Haddock</em></strong> and Sam both are very private about their family. He also has a brother named Joseph Clafin, an actor who has acted in the movie Da Vinci‚Äôs Demons.

