<a href="http://www.wikiceleb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.wikiceleb.com</a>";s:10:"post_title";s:78:"Sam Claflin: Career, Upcoming projects, Personal Life, Achievements, Net worth";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:73:"sam-claflin-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-03-01 22:49:17";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-01 17:04:17";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:28:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=1500";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1512";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-03-02 21:01:16";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-02 15:16:16";s:12:"post_content";s:9358:"<p style="text-align: justify;">She is not only an incredibly fabulous actress but also she is a fierce military recruit which makes this gorgeous badass actress totally different from everyone present in the entertainment world. we are here talking about the one and only¬†<strong><em>Gal Gadot</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Gal Gadot-Varsano</em></strong> was born on 30 April 1985 in a city of Israel, Petah Tikva as a first child to mother Irit who is a teacher and an engineer father Micheal Gadot. She also has a younger sister named Dana Gadot. In high school, Biology was her major subject and began studying at IDC Herzliya College before pursuing her passion for modeling and acting.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>As a model</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1514" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/4506-300x194.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="353" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gadot won the 2004 <strong><em>Miss Israel beauty pageant</em></strong> and then competed in <strong><em>Miss Universe 2004</em></strong> held in Ecuador which marked the beginning of her modeling career. In 2007, she was in Maxim Photo Shoot, <strong><em>‚ÄúWomen of the IDF‚Äù</em></strong> and was featured on the cover of <strong><em>The New York Post</em></strong>.¬† She also has been associated in many Israeli and American campaigns as a model for <strong><em>Miss Sixty</em></strong>, <strong><em>Huawei Smartphones</em></strong>, <strong><em>Gucci fragrances</em></strong>, <strong><em>Vine Vera Skincare ranges</em></strong>, <strong><em>Captain Morgan rum</em></strong> and <strong><em>Jaguar Cars</em></strong>. Then, she was featured as a cover girl in many renowned magazines such as <strong><em>Cosmopolitan</em></strong>, <strong><em>Glamour</em></strong>, <strong><em>Bride Magazine</em></strong>, <strong><em>UMM,</em></strong> <strong><em>Cleo</em></strong>, <strong><em>Entertainment Weekly</em></strong>, <strong><em>Fashion</em></strong>, <strong><em>Lucire </em></strong>and many more. Eventually, from 2008 to 2016 she was the face for fashion brand <strong><em>Castro</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>As an actor</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1515" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wonder_woman_gal_gadot-2048x1536-300x194.jpg" alt="" width="545" height="353" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal Gadot is associated in Television as well. She has acted in some few episodes of television series like <strong><em>Entourage</em></strong> (2009), <strong><em>The Beautiful Life</em></strong> (2009), <strong><em>Asfur</em></strong> (2011), <strong><em>Kathmandu</em></strong> (2012) and <strong><em>Eretz Nehederet </em></strong>(2012).</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The Israeli actress got her first audition call from a cast director for the movie Quantum of Solace but sadly she didn‚Äôt get the role. She then acted in an Israeli film <strong><em>Bubot</em></strong> in 2008. Later, after a few months, she was casted by the same cast director of Quantum of Solace and thus, debuted in Hollywood as Gisele Yashar in the movie <strong><em>Fast and Furious</em></strong> which was the fourth movie in <strong><em>The Fast and Furious Franchise</em></strong> where she splendidly performed all her stunts. She reprised her role in <strong><em>Fast Five</em></strong> as well as <strong><em>Fast and Furious 6</em></strong> in the year 2011 and 2013 respectively.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal then was seen in many movies such as an American comedy movie <strong><em>Date Night</em></strong> (2010), an American action comedy <strong><em>Knight and Day</em></strong> (2010), an Israeli comedy sports film <strong><em>Kicking Out Shoshana </em></strong>(2014), an American crime thriller <strong><em>Triple 9</em></strong> (2016), an American- British action crime thriller <strong><em>Criminal</em></strong> (2016) along with an American action comedy film <strong><em>Keeping Up with the Joneses </em></strong>(2016).</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1517" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/keeping-up-with-the-joneses-2880x1800-jon-hamm-gal-gadot-6205-e1520003345155-300x190.jpg" alt="" width="541" height="342" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Though she had huge potential, she was not able to get roles that would best depict her talent. Later in 2016 she landed the role of Diana Prince/ Wonder Women which proved to be her breakthrough role in the movie <strong><em>Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice</em></strong> under <strong><em>DC Extended Universe</em></strong> which was one of the highest grossing movies of the year. Subsequently, in the following year, she reprised the role in a solo movie <strong><em>Wonder Women</em></strong> and <strong><em>Justice League</em></strong>. Recently, in an interview in <em><strong>Jimmy Kimmel</strong></em> Live she told that she almost didn‚Äôt get her dream role due to her small breasts ergo, Gal had done a lot of physical training to do justice to her superhero role in the movies and consequently the movies were a huge success and her acting and stunt skills were widely acclaimed.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gadot astonishing performance as Wonder Women opened many doors of opportunities in this industry.¬† She is set to reprise her role of Wonder Women in big budget movies <strong><em>Justice League Part 2</em></strong> and <strong><em>Wonder Women Part 2</em></strong> which will be released in 2019. Other than this, she will also be a part of thriller war movie <strong><em>Ruin</em></strong> in 2018. Gal will also be seen in a thriller drama movie <strong><em>Deeper</em></strong> alongside Bradley Cooper and an action adventure fantasy movie <strong><em>Flashpoint,</em></strong> both of which will be released in 2020.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1518" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/landscape-1495182499-gal-gadot-wonder-woman-300x140.jpg" alt="" width="544" height="254" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal Gadot along with her husband <strong><em>Yaron Varsano</em></strong> whom she married in 2008 used to own a luxury hotel in Tel Aviv, Israel until 2015 and now they along with their two beautiful daughters live in Israel. The couple own property in Los Angeles as well.¬† She served for two years in Israel Defense force as a combat instructor. It is also reported that she was 5 months pregnant during reshoots for Wonder Women.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1519" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/5d1e321a64e08954643e15264820d224-300x187.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="335" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gadot has been highly admired for her beauty as well as her acting skills time and again. In 2012 she was ranked on Number 5 on the list of <strong><em>50 most intelligent, funny and gorgeous Jewish Women in the World </em></strong>by Shalom Life. She was awarded <strong><em>Most Popular US Actress in China</em></strong> by <strong><em>Chinese American Film Festival</em></strong> for her role in <strong><em>Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice</em></strong> in 2016. Moreover, Gal‚Äôs role in Wonder Women made her to be honored with <strong><em>Choice Movie: Actress Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>Spotlight Award</em></strong>, <strong><em>Rising Star Award-Actress</em></strong>, and <strong><em>Virtuosos Award</em></strong> from <strong><em>Teen Choice Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>National Board of Review Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>Palm Spring International Film Awards</em></strong> as well as <strong><em>Santa Barbara Film Festival</em></strong> respectively in 2018.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1520" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/653320_thump-300x179.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="320" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Gal Gadot has been ranked in the third position in <strong><em>the highest grossing actor list </em></strong>by Forbes in 2017. She is just behind Vin Diesel and Dwayne Johnson with $1.4 billion in global ticket sales between Wonder Women and Justice League leaving behind her other female stars like <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/daisy-jazz-isobel-ridley-career-future-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Daisy Ridley</a> and Emma Watson. The net worth of Gadot is reported to be $8 million.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Though Gadot had a bumpy journey at the beginning of her career, she is now rising so as to achieve her well-deserved position as one of the A-list actors in Hollywood. This stunning actress has a lot of great movies in her bag and we are pretty sure that this will help her reach spectacular heights in her career.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://www.wikiceleb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.wikiceleb.com</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>";s:10:"post_title";s:75:"Gal Gadot: Career, Upcoming Projects, Personal Life, Achievements, Networth";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:70:"gal-gadot-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:106:"
http://wikiceleb.com/daisy-jazz-isobel-ridley-career-future-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth/";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-03-09 00:44:47";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-08 18:59:47";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:28:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=1512";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1543";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-03-11 23:47:16";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-11 18:02:16";s:12:"post_content";s:7402:"<p style="text-align: justify;">There are quite a few instances where we come up with such talent who leave a huge and strong imprint on the hearts and minds of their fans from a very small age such that the demise of their fictional character would move them to tears ‚Äì the actor we are talking about here is one of the rare talents rising in the industry and he is none other than <strong><em>Chandler Riggs</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>¬†</strong>Born on 27 June 1999 in Atlanta, Georgia-<strong><em>Chandler Riggs</em></strong> is the first child of a businessman father William Riggs and his mother Gina Ann who is a teacher. He was enrolled in a public school named Etwoah High School in Woodstock, Georgia.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Riggs stepped in the entertainment industry when he was quite young. He was seven years old when he made his musical theatre debut at the Atlanta‚Äôs theatre productions of <strong><em>‚ÄúMunchkin‚Äù </em></strong>and <strong><em>‚ÄúThe Wizard of Oz‚Äù.</em></strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1545" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cb97b46b452c3fea646f86597c658b39-carl-grimes-chandler-riggs-300x211.jpg" alt="" width="545" height="383" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">In 2006, Chandler made his first movie debut from <strong><em>‚ÄúJesus H. Zombie‚Äù </em></strong>where he played the role of Egon/Zombie. Then, in the year 2009 he got his first two major roles in a film <strong><em>‚ÄúGet Low‚Äù</em></strong> and a television film <strong><em>‚ÄúThe Wronged Man‚Äù</em></strong>. He has also has done several movies such as,¬† a short film <strong><em>‚ÄúTerminus‚Äù</em></strong> (2011), an American supernatural horror movie <strong><em>‚ÄúMercy‚Äù</em></strong> (2014) along with another American horror movie <strong><em>‚ÄúKeep Watching‚Äù</em></strong> (2017).</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Riggs got his breakthrough role till date as Carl Grimes, son of the lead character Rick Grimes in a popular Television series <strong><em>‚ÄúThe Walking Dead‚Äù</em></strong> which is an AMC horror drama series. The series soon became the highest rated series in the history of cable television and the character of Chandler as Carl was loved by the audiences to bits and he consequently gained immense popularity from it globally. His proficient acting skills in the series were widely praised as well. He had been involved with the series since 2010 and recently in 2018 his character‚Äôs death came as a shock to all his followers Chandler has also been seen in other TV series such as in an episode of an American stop motion sketch comedy <strong><em>‚ÄúRobert Chicken‚Äù</em></strong> (2017) and a live television after show <strong><em>‚ÄúTalking Dead‚Äù</em></strong> (2015-2018) where the host Chris Hardwick talks to the cast of The Walking Dead with guests, celebrity fans and so on.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1546" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/the-walking-dead-season-8-midseason-finale-chandler-riggs-carl-e1520790826182-300x213.jpg" alt="" width="549" height="390" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Furthermore in December 2017 he released his first music album named <strong><em>‚ÄúEclipse‚Äù</em></strong> that was well- received worldwide.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Naturally the recent demise of the beloved character of Carl Grimes played by Chandler Riggs in the famous AMC series The Walking Dead has broken a lot of hearts, but we have a good news that Chandler is set to do much more interesting and intriguing projects. He is set to star in a crime thriller <strong><em>‚ÄúInherit the Viper‚Äù</em></strong> alongside Josh Hartnett, Bruce Dern and Margarita Levieva.¬† The movie is in post-production with no fixed release date as of yet. It also has been announced that he has signed up for a sci-fi film <strong><em>‚ÄúOnly‚Äù</em></strong> alongside Frieda Pinto. Moreover, he may focus more on his musical career as well.¬† Chandler will also be seen in some sequences, conventions, cruises, fan events associated with <strong>The Walking Dead</strong>.</p>
<img class=" wp-image-1547 aligncenter" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/CHANDLER-RIGGS-1500x1020-e1520790943950-300x197.png" alt="" width="541" height="355" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Riggs owns a house in Senoia, Georgia where he lives with his family. He is fond of electric pop music and loves to play videogames and also owns a YouTube channel where he records playing videogames with his friends and his little brother Grayson. He is a humble person and organizes an event to interact with his fans every year. Chandler‚Äôs love life is quite popular as well. He was in a relationship with actress <strong><em>Hana Hayes</em></strong> for two years since 2014 to 2016. After their breakup, he has confirmed to be dating <strong><em>Briana Memphis</em></strong> since 2017. He often is associated with noble charity related events as well. In 2016, he was accepted in Alabama‚Äôs Auburn University but he didn‚Äôt go giving priority to his commitment to The Walking Dead.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1548" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01.16-FILEminimizer-e1520791125142-300x181.jpg" alt="" width="548" height="330" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Being a driven actor, Chandler has been honored with many awards mostly for his popular role in the hit series <strong><em>The Walking Dead</em></strong>. He was awarded with <strong><em>The Best Cast- Television Series Award</em></strong> by <strong><em>Satellite Award</em></strong> in 2012. He also won <strong><em>Best Performance by a Younger Actor in a Television Series </em></strong>twice from <strong><em>Saturn Awards</em></strong> in the year 2013 and 2016. Additionally, in 2014 he won <strong><em>Best Performance in a TV series- Leading Young Actor</em></strong> from <strong><em>Young Artist Awards</em></strong> for his role as Carl Grimes in AMC‚Äôs <strong><em>The Walking Dead</em></strong>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1549" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/saturnawardschandlerriggs2-e1520791275888-300x205.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="369" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Riggs is a well-known teenage heartthrob with a net-worth that is estimated to be over $2 million, where he was earning $1 million from The Walking Dead itself.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Chandler Riggs has established himself as one of the well-known child prodigies in the entertainment world-he still has a lot of years ahead of him and along with a talent that is constantly getting refined and rising upwards he surely won‚Äôt disappoint his fans and is undoubtedly a huge superstar in the making.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>¬†</strong><a href="http://www.wikiceleb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.wikiceleb.com</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>¬†</strong></p>";s:10:"post_title";s:79:"Chandler Riggs Career, Upcoming Projects, Personal Life, Achievements, Networth";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:75:"chandler-riggs-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-03-11 23:48:24";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-11 18:03:24";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:28:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=1543";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1558";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-03-19 00:00:10";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-18 18:15:10";s:12:"post_content";s:11650:"<p style="text-align: justify;">From doing some random itsy-bitsy roles in movies to winning Academy award this actress has come a long way all thanks to her hard work and devotion. The actress we are talking about here is the beautiful and talented <strong><em>Emma Stone</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Emily Jean Stone</em></strong> was born on 6 November 1988 in Scottsdale, Arizona. She was born as a first child to a homemaker mother <em><strong>Krista Stone</strong></em> and <em><strong>J</strong><strong>effery Charles Stone</strong></em> who is CEO of a general contracting company. Firstly, she was educated at Sequoya Elementary School and Cocopah Middle School till sixth grade then she was home-schooled for few years and she was enrolled in Xavier- College preparatory but she dropped out of there and pursed her passion for acting.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Stone commenced her career quite early.¬† She debuted in the acting world at the age of 11 in a stage production of <strong><em>The Wind in the Willows</em></strong> where she played Otter. She also appeared in sixteen productions at <strong><em>Phoneix‚Äôs Valley Youth Theatre</em></strong>. This was the phase where her interest towards acting became stronger. Recently, in 2014-2015 she was back at the theatre for <strong><em>Cabaret</em></strong> where she depicted the role of <em><strong>Sally Bowles</strong></em>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1560" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/6159380-emma-stone-wallpaper-300x193.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="355" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emma has been seen on numerous television shows as well. She got her major television role when she got the role of Laurie Patridge in the TV series <strong><em>The New Patridge Family</em></strong> in 2004. Her acting skills were recognized by people through this role which opened doors for many other small and big roles for her in the television world. In the following years, she appeared in some episodes of TV series such as <strong><em>Medium</em></strong> (2005), <strong><em>Malcolm in the Middle</em></strong> (2005), <strong><em>Lucky Louie</em></strong> (2006), <strong><em>Drive</em></strong> (2007), <strong><em>30 Rock</em></strong> (2012), <strong><em>iCarly</em></strong> (2012). She has also appeared in five episodes of <strong><em>Saturday Night Live!</em></strong> and also has given her voice in <strong><em>Robert Chicken</em></strong> like many renowned actors like <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/nicholas-hoult-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nicholas Hoult</a>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1561" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/emma-stone-wallpaper-night-saturday-wallpapers-300x166.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="309" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emma Stone made her feature film debut in 2007 with a comic movie <strong><em>Superbad</em></strong>. The film was a commercial success and Stone was regarded as an exciting new face in the E-world. Then, she was seen in numerous movies such as an American comedy film <strong><em>The Rocker</em></strong> (2008), a romantic comedy movie <strong><em>The House Bunny</em></strong> (2008), an independent comedy drama movie <strong><em>Paper Man</em></strong> (2009), another romantic comedy film <strong><em>Ghost of Girlfriends Past </em></strong>(2009) alongside Matthew McConaughey, a post-apocalyptic comedy horror movie <strong><em>Zombieland</em></strong> (2009). Among them, Emma was widely praised mostly for the latter two where Zombieland with an earnings of more than $100 million became a high grossing movie.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1562" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/d97572138638b7dad5f2c2e54049605e-300x178.jpg" alt="" width="553" height="328" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">In the succeeding years, Stone acted in many commercial and critically acclaimed movies like a teen comedy flick <strong><em>Easy A</em></strong> (2010), <strong><em>Friends with Benefits</em></strong> (2011), a romantic comedy movie <strong><em>Crazy Stupid Love </em></strong>(2011), an American period drama <strong><em>The Help</em></strong> (2011). The acting skills of Emma was regarded as the prime asset of all the movies.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">One of the breakthrough roles of Stone was in the movie <strong><em>The Amazing Spider Man</em></strong>(2012) where she portrayed the role of <em><strong>Gwen Stacy</strong></em>, love interest of the title character.¬† She reprised the same role in <strong><em>The Amazing Spider Man 2</em></strong> (2014) alongside <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/andrew-garfield-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Andrew Garfield</a>. Both the movies were one of the highest grossing movies in the respective year. Moreover, she was a part of the Academy award winning movie <strong><em>Birdman</em></strong> (2014) alongside Micheal Keaton and Edward Norton. She further appeared in an anthrology comedy <strong><em>Movie 43</em></strong> (2013),¬† an action crime film <strong><em>Gangster Squad</em></strong> (2013), <strong><em>Magic in the Moonlight</em></strong> (2014), <strong><em>Aloha</em></strong> (2015), crime drama film <strong><em>Irrational Man</em></strong> (2015) and a mockumentary comedy <strong><em>Popstar</em></strong> (2016).</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1563" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Emma-Stone-Amazing-Spider-Man-Wallpaper-e1521395041736-300x182.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="334" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Another major role of Stone was in the movie <strong><em>La La Land</em></strong> in 2016 which is a romantic musical movie alongside Ryan Gosling. The movie was a huge success globally earning over $400 million in box-office and Emma received highly positive views by the audiences. Later in 2017, she featured in a sports drama movie <strong><em>Battle of the Sexes</em></strong> which was another acclaimed movie of Stone.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Being an extremely driven actress Emma Stone has lots of projects with her. She is set to play in a historical drama movie <strong><em>The Favourite</em></strong> which will be released in 2018.¬† Emma will also be seen in a drama movie <strong><em>Love May Fail</em></strong> which is based on a 2015 novel by Matthew Quick. Additionally, she will feature as Cruella de Vil in a live- action spin off of <strong><em>One Hundered and One Dalmations</em></strong>. She will also act as well as produce for an upcoming Netflix series <strong><em>Maniac</em></strong> which will be broadcasted in 2018.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1564" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/actress_emma_stone-1920x1200-300x182.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="331" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emma used to reside in Greenwich Village, New York but moved back to Los Angeles in 2016. She shares a close relationship with her family. She has mentioned in her interviews that she made a PowerPoint presentation titled ‚ÄúProject Hollywood‚Äù in order to convince her parents to let her pursue a career in acting. She suffered from panic attacks and asthma in past. Though she has appeared as a red head in most of her movies, she is actually blonde weighing 52 kgs. She dated her The Amazing Spiderman co-star <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/andrew-garfield-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong><em>Andrew Garfield</em></strong></a> for five years. The couple broke-up in 2015. She belongs to Lutheranism religion. She claims tom Hanks and Jesse Eisenberg to be her favorite actors. She is also a Basketball enthusiast.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1565" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/emma-stone-andrew-garfield-cuddle-up-in-nyc-02-e1521395694536-300x209.jpg" alt="" width="543" height="379" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Stone is one of the most talented actresses of her generation. She has been adorned universally for both her beauty and acting skills. In 2010, <strong><em>LoveFilm</em></strong> kept her on the list of <strong><em>Top 20 Actresses under 30</em></strong>. She was also featured in <strong><em>Times Magazine</em></strong> as one of the <strong><em>100 most influential people of the world</em></strong> in 2017 and in the same year she was declared as one of the <strong><em>world‚Äôs most beautiful women</em></strong> by <strong><em>Buzznet</em></strong>. As far as her acting career is concerned she has been nominated and has also won numerous prestigious awards. Emma won <strong><em>The Oscars Best Actress award</em></strong> for her performance in the movie <strong><em>La La Land</em></strong> in 2017. She also won <strong><em>Best Actress in a Leading role award</em></strong> for the same movie in the same year by <strong><em>Australian Academy of television Arts Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>British Academy Film Awards </em></strong>and<strong><em> Golden Globes Awards</em></strong>. Furthermore, she achieved <strong><em>Ensemble of the Year award</em></strong>,<strong><em> Best acting by an Ensemble</em></strong>,<strong><em> Favorite Movie Actress</em></strong>,<strong><em> Best Cast- Motion Picture Award by Hollywood films Awards</em></strong>,<strong><em> National Board of Review People‚Äôs choice Awards </em></strong>and<strong><em> Satellite Awards</em></strong> respectively for her movie <strong><em>The Help</em></strong> in 2012. She also won <strong><em>MTV Movie and TV awards</em></strong> for <strong><em>Best Comedic Performance</em></strong> in the movie <strong><em>Easy A</em></strong> in 2011. ¬†Likewise, she earned three <strong><em>Screen Actors Guild Awards </em></strong>for her <strong><em>Outstanding Performances</em></strong> in the movies <strong><em>The Help</em></strong> (2012), <strong><em>Birdman</em></strong> (2015) and <strong><em>La La Land</em></strong> (2017).</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1566" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/emma-stone-2177x1225-academy-award-oscar-awards-2017-6480-300x186.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="338" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth: How Rich is Emma Stone?</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Stone has been named the world‚Äôs highest paid actress by <strong><em>Forbes Magazine</em></strong> in 2017 outranking last year‚Äôs list topper and her good friend Jennifer Lawrence. With the boost from <strong><em>La La Land</em></strong>, the net worth of Emma Stone is reported to be $28 million.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emma Stone is claimed to be one of the biggest names in the industry today, she has been able to reach such heights with great hardship and effort. She is absolutely incredible in sole movies and also is able to mark her presence in an ordinary supporting role as well. Emma is loved by her fans and with lots of promising projects in her pocket we are sure she will continue to be on top in future as well.</p>
